OL,3,CCarbon monoxide detectors to be sold
OL,4,Cin airports two years after man's death
OL,6,FThe level of carbon monoxide in his
OL,7,Fblood was 51.75% - normal levels in
OL,8,Fhealthy adults range between 0 to 5%.
OL,10,FSince then, Hudson's family have been
OL,11,Fencouraging others to take an alarm
OL,12,Fwith them as part of the 'Pack Safe
OL,13,FAppeal.'
OL,15,FThe Foreign Office doesn't mandate all
OL,16,Ftravellers to take a carbon monoxide
OL,17,Falarm, but it does advise packing a
OL,18,Fdetector for any accommodation, such
OL,19,Fas a hotel, holiday home, or caravan.
