OL,3,CCarbon monoxide detectors to be sold
OL,4,Cin airports two years after man's death
OL,6,FFrom 28 August, portable carbon
OL,7,Fmonoxide alarms will go on sale across
OL,8,F14 UK airports for the very first
OL,9,Ftime, including Heathrow, Gatwick,
OL,10,FManchester and Edinburgh.
OL,12,FCampaigners call this is a milestone
OL,13,Fin travel safety, saying with
OL,14,F'travellers finally being able to buy
OL,15,Falarms before boarding, with ignored
OL,16,Fwarnings now being acted on.'
